    <item>
      <title>英美烟草公司称非法电子烟导致美国电子烟销量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/british-american-tobacco-cites-illicit-vapes-for-slower-us-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美烟草公司无烟产品的增长受到美国市场非法电子烟盛行的拖累，迫使该烟草制造商提供令人失望的 2025 年业绩预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/british-american-tobacco-cites-illicit-vapes-for-slower-us-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:03:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡拟出台税收优惠措施以振兴股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/singapore-moots-tax-incentives-to-revive-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由新加坡政府牵头的审查小组提议采取税收激励措施来重振股市，这是在流动性低、新股上市稀缺的市场中采取的第一步措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/singapore-moots-tax-incentives-to-revive-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:02:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Neste 计划裁员 600 人，取消股息政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/neste-plans-to-cut-600-jobs-cancels-dividend-in-turnaround-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Neste Oyj 取消了其股息政策，并宣布计划裁员约 600 人，因为这家可再生燃料生产商认为今年市场“供应过剩，因此面临挑战”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/neste-plans-to-cut-600-jobs-cancels-dividend-in-turnaround-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 08:47:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华选择阿姆斯特丹而非伦敦作为冰淇淋主要上市地点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/unilever-sees-modest-profitability-boost-in-2025-starts-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合利华 (Unilever Plc) 表示，其冰淇淋部门将主要在阿姆斯特丹上市，而当 Ben &amp; Jerry’s 的生产商今年分拆后，伦敦和纽约将作为第二上市地点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/unilever-sees-modest-profitability-boost-in-2025-starts-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 07:12:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普“令人震惊”的贸易局势令印尼寻求新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼贸易部副部长迪亚·罗罗·埃斯蒂·维迪亚·普特里表示，随着全球保护主义愈演愈烈，印尼正寻求实现市场多元化，同时也采取措施保护本土制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 02:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
